<h4 class="widget-title widgettitle">Announcement Area</h4>
<article class="post-4189 post type-post status-publish format-standard category-announcements entry"><div class="entry-content">
<div style="height:43px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<div class="wp-block-columns">
<div class="wp-block-column">
<div class="wp-block-group"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3>Virtual Board Meeting</h3>



<p><strong>Join us on Monday, April 20th, the Bridgman Board of Education Meeting will be online @ 6:30 p.m. </strong></p>



<div class="wp-block-buttons">
<div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link has-text-color has-background has-vivid-cyan-blue-background-color" href="https://bridgmanschools.zoom.us/j/95350482119?pwd=Y3VmRnhFR2xLVVhDK2dLNkI4a29qQT09" style="color:#ffffff">Click here to attend</a></div>
</div>
</div></div>
</div>



<div class="wp-block-column"></div>
</div>



<div style="height:43px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<hr class="wp-block-separator">
<h3>Given the recent conversations surrounding Coronavirus (COVID-19), we felt this information should be shared with our school family.  </h3>



<hr class="wp-block-separator">
<div class="wp-block-file">
<a href="https://bridgmanschools.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bridgman-Continuity-of-Learning-and-COVID-19-Response-Plan-.pdf">Bridgman Continuity of Learning and COVID-19 Response Plan</a><a href="https://bridgmanschools.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bridgman-Continuity-of-Learning-and-COVID-19-Response-Plan-.pdf" class="wp-block-file__button" download>Download</a>
</div>



<div class="wp-block-file">
<a href="https://bridgmanschools.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bridgman-ISD-Approval-Guide.pdf">Bridgman ISD Approval Guide</a><a href="https://bridgmanschools.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bridgman-ISD-Approval-Guide.pdf" class="wp-block-file__button" download>Download</a>
</div>



<hr class="wp-block-separator">
<div class="wp-block-columns">
<div class="wp-block-column">
<div class="wp-block-group"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3>Educational &amp; Enrichment Opportunities</h3>



<p><strong>While this certainly isn’t a comprehensive list, these are some resources that we have found to be useful and fun.</strong></p>



<div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link has-text-color has-background has-vivid-cyan-blue-background-color" href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1RABnzWy6R9hzgpmoljsHAM8StkkqnHRQxHu5PhdqNNg/edit?usp=sharing" style="color:#ffffff">Resources</a></div>
</div></div>
</div>



<div class="wp-block-column">
<div class="wp-block-group"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3>Frequently Asked Questions</h3>



<p>Questions about what’s happening with COVD-19 and how it will impact your family?  Please read the frequently updated document below, we hope this provides some needed answers.</p>



<div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link has-text-color has-background has-vivid-cyan-blue-background-color" href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1LjrSOhsNiQGccdeicon5OInqGdehJ_NBO7aXL62CCek/edit?usp=sharing" style="color:#ffffff">More Information</a></div>
</div></div>
</div>
</div>



<hr class="wp-block-separator">
<div class="wp-block-columns">
<div class="wp-block-column" style="flex-basis:66.66%">
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><a href="https://www.helpmegrow-mi.org/essential" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><img src="https://bridgmanschools.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/image003.png" alt="Click here for Disaster Relief Child Care Services for Michigan's Essential Workforce." class="wp-image-4267" srcset="https://bridgmanschools.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/image003.png 472w, https://bridgmanschools.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/image003-300x300.png 300w, https://bridgmanschools.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/image003-150x150.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 472px) 100vw, 472px"></a></figure>
</div>



<div class="wp-block-column" style="flex-basis:33.33%">
<div class="wp-block-file">
<a href="https://bridgmanschools.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Child-Care-Flyer-reduced-file-size.pdf">Child Care Flyer</a><a href="https://bridgmanschools.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Child-Care-Flyer-reduced-file-size.pdf" class="wp-block-file__button" download>Download</a>
</div>



<div class="wp-block-file">
<a href="https://bridgmanschools.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/News-Release-Child-Care-for-Essential-Workers-3-23-2020.pdf">News Release (Child Care for Essential Workers) 3-23-2020</a><a href="https://bridgmanschools.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/News-Release-Child-Care-for-Essential-Workers-3-23-2020.pdf" class="wp-block-file__button" download>Download</a>
</div>



<p>More information is available on the Berrien RESA website:<br><a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://www.berrienresa.org/cms/One.aspx?portalId=148604&amp;pageId=7505580" target="_blank">Coronavirus Information from Berrien RESA</a> </p>
</div>
</div>



<hr class="wp-block-separator">
<div class="wp-block-file">
<a href="https://bridgmanschools.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Spanish-Coronavirus.pdf">Nuevo Coronavirus</a><a href="https://bridgmanschools.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Spanish-Coronavirus.pdf" class="wp-block-file__button" download>Download</a>
</div>



<div class="wp-block-file">
<a href="https://bridgmanschools.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/COVID-19-Letter-to-Parents-342020.pdf">Parent Letter: Coronavirus</a><a href="https://bridgmanschools.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/COVID-19-Letter-to-Parents-342020.pdf" class="wp-block-file__button" download>Download</a>
</div>



<hr class="wp-block-separator">
<div class="wp-block-columns">
<div class="wp-block-column">
<h3><strong>Social/Emotional Resources</strong></h3>



<p>If your student is struggling emotionally during this time, please take a moment to view the many resources available in our area that may provide assistance. <a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1W0oHS9zST6jS0trIGt-xrDpYe8btKLSv9xsOEkvFl2c/edit?usp=sharing"><strong>More Information … </strong></a></p>



<p>Bridgman Public Schools has established a specific email address <strong><a href="mailto:info@bridgmanschools.com">info@bridgmanschools.com</a></strong> to address any concerns or additional resources that your child or your family might have during the COVID-19 School Closure. Please reach out to us if you need additional support or assistance. </p>
</div>



<div class="wp-block-column">
<h3>
<strong>Food Service </strong><br>
</h3>



<p>Bridgman Public Schools will continue to provide nutritious breakfast and lunches at Bridgman High School on <strong>Wednesdays from 5pm – 7pm </strong>during the Bridgman Public Schools closure.  This service is FREE to all children 18 years old and younger.   <br></p>
</div>
</div>
</div></article>
